title: XNY - Orange [2013]
description:
I tried to buy this album and found it's no longer available anywhere. I managed to find it on a couple streaming services that still had it and put this album together myself. Now even those are gone, so I'm sharing this torrent. I have no idea why XNY has been practically scrubbed from the Internet, but their music is amazing and people should hear it!

"Pam Autuori (vox/guitar) and Jacob Shreiber (drums) met as next door neighbors while attending Berklee College of Music in Boston, Massachusetts. Formulating a catchy, dance-inspired rock sound, infused with blues and punk undertones, combined with witty, anecdotal lyrics and driving, dynamic rhythms, XNY has supported Hunter Hunted, Reptar and Styx; in addition to headlining festivals and shows in notable venues (i.e. The Knitting Factory, The Studio at Webster Hall, Rockwood Music Hall, etc.)."
